The county government center in Las Vegas , Clark County, Nevada , 15th most populous county in the United States.
List of the most populous counties in the United States
Seattle seat of King County, Washington , King County ranks as the 14th most populous county in the United States.
[ edit ] List of most populous counties
The Guardian Building , headquarters of Michigan's Wayne County , 13th most populous county in the United States.
Downtown Miami in Miami-Dade County , the largest county in Florida, and the county seat of the 8th most populous county in the United States.
Row houses in Brooklyn , Kings County , New York , the 7th most populous county in the United States.
Aerial view of Orange County, California , the 5th most populous county in the United States.
Downtown Phoenix, Arizona , county seat of the fourth most populous county in the United States, Maricopa County , Arizona.
The Wortham Center in Houston , county seat of Harris County, Texas , the third most populous county in the United States.
